Privacy Policy for Speed Reading Trainer Extension
Last Updated: 11/17/2024
Introduction
This Privacy Policy explains how the Speed Reading Trainer Extension ("we", "our", or "the extension") collects, uses, and protects your information when you use our browser extension.
Information We Collect
Our extension collects and processes the following types of information:
a) User Activity: We collect data on how you interact with the extension, including when you activate the speed reading feature and your reading speed settings.
b) Website Content: To provide the speed reading functionality, we temporarily process the text content you select on web pages. This content is not stored or transmitted outside of your browser.
c) Settings: We store your preferences, such as words per minute and font size, to personalize your experience.
d) Payment Information: For premium features, payment processing is handled by ExtensionPay. They may collect personal and financial information necessary for transactions. Please refer to ExtensionPay's privacy policy for details on their data handling practices.
How We Use Your Information
We use the collected information to:
Provide and improve the speed reading functionality
Personalize your experience based on your settings
Process payments and manage subscriptions for premium features
Analyze usage to improve the extension's performance and features
Data Storage and Security
Your settings are stored locally in your browser using secure browser storage mechanisms. We do not transmit or store your personal data or browsing history on our servers.
Third-Party Services
We use ExtensionPay for payment processing. Their use of your information is governed by their privacy policy. We encourage you to review their policy for details on their data handling practices.
Your Rights
You have the right to:
Access the personal information we hold about you
Request correction of any inaccurate information
Request deletion of your data
Opt-out of any future communications from us
To exercise these rights, please contact us at [Your Contact Email].
Changes to This Policy
We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new policy on this page.
